A local female DJ has been accused of being a home-wrecker after having a secret affair with a senior manager at a certain bank. The DJ, who boasts good looks and gets several gigs a week, has been sleeping around with the manager, knowing very well the boss is a married man. Recently, the man went with the DJ to his house and battered his wife, who had given birth through C-section, in front of their children. The DJ could not even intervene to stop her sponsor, despite being the one who caused the fight. Instead, the following day, she was narrating it to her evil friends, forgetting that a man who is a wife batterer is a dangerous animal who will also beat her up some day. The boss has even chased his legal wife from their matrimonial home, and the DJ was overheard bragging shamelessly to her friends about it.